-- Aviva Investors Names Robert James as Its Pan European Financials Analyst
-- Francesca Cinelli
-- 2010-07-29T09:59:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/aviva-investors-names-robert-james-as-its-pan-european-financials-analyst.html

          
          
             Aviva Investors, the asset
management unit of  Aviva Plc , named Robert James as Pan European
Financials Analyst.  
 Before joining Aviva Investors, James worked as a banking
analyst at Insight Investment, the London-based company said in
an e-mailed statement today.  
 James will report to Davis Lis, head of U.K. Equities, and
 John Botham , head of European Equities.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
 Francesca Cinelli  in Milan at 
 fcinelli@bloomberg.net .  
          
          


  


        